# 🎮 Tic Tac Toe Game

A modern and interactive **Tic Tac Toe** game built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. This project includes multiple game modes, beautiful UI, sound effects, animations, dark mode, timer, score tracking, and AI opponents, making it an excellent beginner-to-intermediate JavaScript project.

