# 🎮 How to Play

1. Open the game in your browser.
2. Select your preferred game mode.
3. Click on any empty box to make your move.
4. Align three symbols horizontally, vertically, or diagonally to win.
5. Use the Reset or New Game button to play again.

---

# 🤖 AI Modes

### 👥 Player vs Player
Two players take turns playing on the same device.

### 🤖 Easy AI
The computer selects random available positions.

### 🧠 Hard AI
Powered by the **Minimax Algorithm**, making the AI nearly impossible to defeat.

---

# 🏆 Winning Rules

A player wins by placing three identical symbols in:

- Horizontal Row
- Vertical Column
- Diagonal

If all boxes are filled without a winner, the game ends in a draw.

---

# 📊 Score System

The game automatically tracks:

- Player X Wins
- Player O Wins
- Draw Matches

Scores are stored using **Local Storage**, so they remain available even after refreshing the browser.

---

# 🌙 Dark Mode

Switch between:

- ☀️ Light Theme
- 🌙 Dark Theme

Your selected theme is automatically saved.

---

