# 📱 Responsive Design

The game works smoothly on:

- Desktop
- Laptop
- Tablet
- Mobile Devices

---

# 🧠 Minimax Algorithm

The Hard AI uses the **Minimax Algorithm**, allowing it to:

- Predict future moves
- Block the player's winning chances
- Choose the optimal move
- Never intentionally lose

---

# 📦 Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/tic-tac-toe.git
```

Go to the project folder

```bash
cd tic-tac-toe
```

Open

```
index.html
```

in your browser.

